The module can be loaded manually by typing
modload ${PREFIX}/lkm/nv.o

In order to load it automatically at boot time,
- Add to your /etc/rc.conf file:
lkm=YES

- Add to your /etc/lkm.conf:
${PREFIX}/lkm/nv.o   -        -          -          -       BEFORENET

===========================================================================
